title: Chelsea vs. Manchester United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Chelsea have won just one of their last 14 Premier League games against Manchester United, though it was a 4-3 victory in this exact fixture last season. Manchester United have won just one of their last 11 Premier League away games against Chelsea, a 2-0 victory in February 2020 under Ole Gunnar Solskjaer.

title: Barcelona vs Real Madrid - Spanish La Liga 2023/2024
description: Barcelona have won their last three matches against Real Madrid in all competitions, only once in the entire history of ElClásico, between 2008 and 2010 under Josep Guardiola, have the Blaugrana managed 4+ consecutive wins. Real Madrid have won four of their last five away matches against FC Barcelona in all competitions, achieving the same number of victories as in their previous 19 visits to Barcelona.

title: Newcastle United vs Chelsea - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Newcastle have won seven of their last 11 Premier League home games against Chelsea, including both under manager Eddie Howe. Chelsea have won 31 Premier League games against Newcastle, only beating Tottenham and West Ham more often in the competition.

title: Liverpool vs Arsenal - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Liverpool are unbeaten in their last 14 home games against Arsenal in all competitions since a 2-0 loss in the Premier League in September 2012. Arsenal are unbeaten in their last five Premier League games against Liverpool, their longest run without defeat against the Reds since a run of eight between October 2007 and April 2011.

title: Everton vs. Southampton - English Premier League 2024/2025

Following their 1-0 win at St Mary’s in the reverse fixture, Southampton are looking to complete the league double over Everton for the first time since 1997-98.

description: A recap of the best of the action, plus a look forward to the next Match Day in Europe’s premium football competition, the UEFA Champions League. This season is the first in the new format, with 36 participating teams in a league phase replacing the previous Group stage. All matches from the UEFA Champions League are live and exclusive only on beIN.

title: In The Footsteps of Beraldo
description: As a child, Lucas Beraldo visited the Parc des Princes alongside his brother, his eyes filled with dreams. He imagined himself, one day, playing here... in the PSG jersey.

title: Nice vs Brest - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Nice have lost only one of their last eight Ligue 1 games against Brest. The last five Nice-Brest matches in Ligue 1 have produced just three goals, or 0.6 per game, the lowest average among meetings played in each of the last three seasons. Nice have won five of their last six matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, sharing the points in their most recent one. The last defeat of OGCN to end a season in the top-flight dates to 2017-18.

title: Atletico Madrid vs Real Betis - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Atletico de Madrid have not lost any of their last 11 home games against Real Betis in LaLiga, winning the last six, the best run of consecutive home wins against the green-and-white side in their entire history in the competition. title: PSG vs Auxerre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Paris SG have not lost any of their last five matches against Auxerre in Ligue 1. PSG are also unbeaten in their last 37 home games against a promoted side in Ligue 1 – scoring an average of 2.9 goals – since a defeat against Montpellier in their last match of the 2009-10 season. The last draw between Paris SG and Auxerre at the Parc des Princes in Ligue 1 was in December 2001. Since then, the 11 clashes between the two teams in the top-flight have seen eight wins for Paris and three for Auxerre.

title: Nantes vs Montpellier - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Nantes have won 64.3% of their Ligue 1 home games against Montpellier in the 21st century, their highest success rate against an opponent they have faced 10+ times on home soil during this period. title: Hoffenheim vs Bayern Munchen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: Since the start of 2016/17, TSG Hoffenheim have collected 13 points in eight Bundesliga home games against FC Bayern Munchen – only Borussia Monchengladbach have picked up as many home points against FCB during this time. TSG beat Bayern 4-2 from 2-0 down on the final matchday last season. 32 points from 33 games represents the second-worst Bundesliga season in TSG Hoffenheim’s history – they have only ever been worse off in 2012/13 when they stayed up via the relegation play-off. TSG have won just one of their last nine league games : 2-0 at home against Mainz in mid-April.

title: Borussia Monchengladbach vs Wolfsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: VfL Wolfsburg recorded their joint-biggest win in the Bundesliga this season in the reverse fixture against Borussia Monchengladbach – the Wolves could now do a league double over the Foals for the first time since 2009/10. VfL Wolfsburg are winless in their last nine Bundesliga games, the longest ongoing wait in the league and the Wolves’ longest spell without victory since between December 2023 and March 2024. Wolfsburg are also without a clean sheet in their last 12 Bundesliga matches, currently the worst run in the league.

title: Freiburg vs Eintracht Frankfurt - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: This fixture is SC Freiburg’s 850th Bundesliga match. SC Freiburg have picked up 13 of a possible 15 points over the last five matchdays, a joint league high together with Borussia Dortmund. Eintracht Frankfurt have also remained unbeaten during this period, conceding the joint-fewest goals in the league.

title: Bundesliga Highlights 2024/25 Week 34
description: Each Bundesliga Matchweek is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

title: Borussia Dortmund vs Holstein Kiel - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: Holstein Kiel and Borussia Dortmund have met three times so far: BVB won 4-0 away in the quarter-finals of the 2011/12 DFB-Pokal and then 5-0 at home in the semi-finals in 2020/21, before the Storks won 4-2 in this season’s reverse fixture. It was Dortmund’s first defeat against a Bundesliga debutant since August 2019. Borussia Dortmund have won four Bundesliga games in a row for the first time since March 2024. They have picked up 19 of a possible 21 points from the last seven matchdays, a league high.

title: Mainz 05 vs Bayer Leverkusen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: 1. FSV Mainz 05 have lost 11 of their 14 Bundesliga games against Bayer 04 Leverkusen since the start of 2018 – the Werkself haven’t beaten any other side more often during this period and the 05ers haven’t suffered more defeats against any other side. Leverkusen have won each of the last three meetings. Bayer 04 Leverkusen have only won one of their last five Bundesliga games. 68 points from 33 games is still their third-best record in the top flight. Last weekend’s 4-2 defeat against Borussia Dortmund saw them concede more than three goals in a Bundesliga game for the first time since October 2022.

title: Mallorca vs Getafe - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Mallorca have not lost any of their last four games against Getafe in LaLiga, equalling their best unbeaten run against them in the top-flight, achieved in their first four meetings between 2004 and 2006. Getafe have taken points in five of their last six LaLiga away games against Mallorca, this after having lost six of their first seven visits to the island in the competition.

title: Main Race - France Round- Moto 3
description: The lightweight class lines up for the main race at the iconic Le Mans circuit. Riders tackle 22 laps of high-intensity action, with close slipstreaming and bold overtakes expected throughout. Precision, bravery, and race craft will define the battle for victory and championship points.

title: Main Race - France Round - Moto 2
description: The intermediate class takes center stage at Le Mans for the sixth round of the 2025 season. Riders will navigate 22 laps of the 4.2 km Bugatti Circuit, aiming to master its technical layout and secure vital championship points. Expect intense competition and strategic overtakes as the Moto2 field battles for supremacy on this iconic French track.

title: Main Race - France GP - Moto GP
description: The premier class of motorcycle racing returns to the iconic Le Mans Bugatti Circuit for Round 6 of the season. Riders battle over 27 laps on the technical 4.2 km layout, known for its tight corners and unpredictable conditions. Expect high-speed duels, bold overtakes, and fierce competition as the championship fight intensifies in front of passionate French fans.

title: DTM Show 2025 -Oschersleben
description: The DTM season roars into Oschersleben as top touring car drivers battle it out on one of Germany’s most technical circuits. High-speed drama, precision racing, and fierce rivalries take center stage in this thrilling round of the 2025 championship.

title: Race 1 - Oschersleben Round - ADAC GT4 Germany 2025
description: The 2025 ADAC GT4 Germany season launches at Motorsport Arena Oschersleben with a thrilling Race 1. Enrico Forderer and Jay Mo Hartling deliver a strong performance to take the opening win, as fierce battles unfold across the grid, setting the stage for an intense season ahead.

title: Race 2 - Oschersleben Round - ADAC GT4 Germany 2025
description: The action continues at Oschersleben with Race 2 of the ADAC GT4 Germany season. After an intense opener, teams battle for early momentum and crucial championship points.

title: Race 1 - Oschersleben Round - DTM - 2025
description: The 2025 DTM season kicks off at the iconic Motorsport Arena Oschersleben. In Race 1, the championship’s top drivers and manufacturers go head-to-head, launching a thrilling new season of speed, strategy, and fierce on-track battles. Expectations are high as new line-ups and fresh rivalries set the stage for an unforgettable start.

title: Race 2 - Oschersleben Round - DTM - 2025
description: The DTM season continues at Motorsport Arena Oschersleben with Race 2. Top drivers and manufacturers battle for crucial championship points in what promises to be another thrilling showdown on the challenging German circuit.

title: Race 1 - Formula 4 Italy - Misano Round - 2025
description: The 2025 Italian F4 Championship roars to life at the Misano World Circuit. In Race 1, a grid packed with ambitious young talent takes to the track for the seasons opening battle. With nerves high and margins tight, every move counts in the quest for early momentum and points.

title: Race 2 - Formula 4 Italy - Misano Round - 2025
description: Race 2 of the Misano weekend intensifies the fight for supremacy in the Italian F4 Championship. Drivers adjust strategies and sharpen their focus after Race 1, aiming to climb the standings in a fast-paced, highly tactical contest under pressure.

title: Race 3 - Formula 4 Italy - Misano Round - 2025
description: The final showdown at Misano sees the field go all out in Race 3, where consistency and courage could decide the weekend’s overall winner. With podiums and crucial points at stake, expect a dramatic and decisive finale in this opening round of the 2025 season.

title: Sprint Race - F1 Miami Grand Prix - 2025
description: beIN SPORTS is the live and exclusive broadcast partners of Formula 1 until end of 2033 season. title: Race 1 - F1 Academy 2025 - Miami Round

title: Qualifying - Imola Round - Porsche SuperCup - 2025

title: Race - Imola Round - Porsche SuperCup - 2025

Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament.
